text: The Ka'a'gee Tu First Nation is a Dene First Nations band government in the Northwest Territories. The band is headquartered in the community of Kakisa, the smallest in the territory. The Ka'a'gee Tu First Nation is a member of the Dehcho First Nations. ==References== Category:First Nations in the Northwest Territories Category:Dene governments
title: Ka'a'gee Tu First Nation
